{"id": "art-25171", "label": "Art. 25171", "title": "Art. 25171", "slug": "art-25171", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_592330246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1261\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_592330246\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>71</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1149064540\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1260\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1149064540\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În termen de 45 de zile de la data efectu&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> proiectului de divizare, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>67</sup>, orice creditor a\nc&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span> este anterioar&#259;\nacestei date <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nescadent&#259; la aceast&#259;\ndat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care este <span class=SpellE>nemul&#355;umit</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> acordate prin proiectul de\ndivizare notific&#259; societatea pentru acordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>\nadecvate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2024610984\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1259\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2024610984\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În termen de 15 zile de la împlinirea termenului\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1), societatea transmite creditorului oferta privind\nacordarea de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1397270820\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1258\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1397270820\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care creditorul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1)\nnu consider&#259; adecvate <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> acordate\nde societate, se poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> pentru\nobligarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> la acordarea de <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> adecvate, dac&#259; creditorul <span\nclass=SpellE>dovede&#351;te</span>, în mod rezonabil, c&#259; divizarea\nafecteaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;ansele</span> de acoperire a <span\nclass=SpellE>crean&#355;ei</span>. <span class=SpellE>Garan&#355;iile</span>\nsunt acordate sub <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca divizarea s&#259;\nproduc&#259; efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1295419582\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1257\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1295419582\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cererea se depune, în termen de 3 luni de la data\nefectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span> potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>67</sup>, la oficiul\nregistrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> de la sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul diviz&#259;rii, care,\nîn termen de 3 zile de la data depunerii, o <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîn registru <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> o înainteaz&#259; tribunalului în\na c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. La cerere se anexeaz&#259; dovada\nnotific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în vederea\nconstituirii de <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, oferta <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nHot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este executorie <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> este supus&#259; numai apelului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_439642449\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1256\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_439642449\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Cererea creditorului se judec&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu\nprec&#259;dere. Dac&#259; sunt formulate mai multe cereri, acestea se\nconexeaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_385766763\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1255\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_385766763\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Certificatul prealabil diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere\npoate fi emis numai dac&#259; societatea prezint&#259; dovezi privind\nacceptarea de c&#259;tre creditori a <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span>\nconstituite ca urmare a notific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau potrivit hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_982425569\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1254\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_982425569\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nromân&#259; este <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i>\naplicabil&#259; cererilor creditorilor formulate potrivit alin. (1), iar\ntribunalul în a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se\nafl&#259; sediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face\nobiectul diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere este <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\ncompetent&#259; s&#259; <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ioneze</span> cererile\nacestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1468302554\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1253\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1468302554\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Pe o perioad&#259; de 2 ani de la data la care produce\nefecte divizarea transfrontalier&#259;, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>76</sup>, orice cerere a oric&#259;rui creditor care <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> o <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>\nanterioar&#259; datei efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nproiectului de divizare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nescadent&#259; la\nacea dat&#259;, în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu acea <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>,\npoate fi adresat&#259; <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> competente în a\nc&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> teritorial&#259; a\navut sediul social societatea care a f&#259;cut obiectul diviz&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1448597567\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1252\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1448597567\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 172 alin. (1) lit. d), <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (1)-(8) sunt aplicabile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_838092476\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1251\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_838092476\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)În cazul în care o <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;&#259;</span>\na unui creditor al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face\nobiectul diviz&#259;rii nu este acoperit&#259; de societatea c&#259;reia îi\neste alocat&#259; <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span> corelativ&#259;,\ncelelalte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> beneficiare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, în cazul unei diviz&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>par&#355;iale</span>\nsau al unei diviz&#259;ri prin separare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nsocietatea care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii r&#259;spund în solidar cu\nsocietatea c&#259;reia îi este alocat&#259; <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span>.\nCu toate acestea, suma maxim&#259; aferent&#259; r&#259;spunderii în solidar a\noric&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> implicate în\ndivizare este limitat&#259; la valoarea, la data la care divizarea produce\nefecte, a activului net alocat respectivei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>.</span></p>"}